1
00:01:30,575 --> 00:01:35,805
(Flourished Peony)

2
00:01:35,886 --> 00:01:39,000
(Episode 20)

3
00:01:41,368 --> 00:01:43,188
No wonder the business of Huanyun Pavilion is always good.

4
00:01:44,119 --> 00:01:46,080
The bed is so comfortable.

5
00:01:50,232 --> 00:01:51,760
Actually, tonight,

6
00:01:52,390 --> 00:01:54,360
I've been wanting to find an opportunity

7
00:01:55,088 --> 00:01:56,800
to have a good chat with you.

8
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,600
What do you want to know, Mu Dan?

9
00:01:58,741 --> 00:02:00,360
I will tell you everything you want to know.

10
00:02:00,831 --> 00:02:01,831
That's great.

11
00:02:02,608 --> 00:02:04,158
I dared not disturb you

12
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:05,880
when I saw how busy you were today.

13
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:08,426
Thankfully, there are not enough rooms

14
00:02:08,511 --> 00:02:10,738
so I can shamelessly enter your room

15
00:02:10,819 --> 00:02:12,800
and learn about business from you.

16
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,101
You are also a shopowner.

17
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,101
Blooming Abode's business is booming.

18
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,900
What else do you need to know?

19
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,420
There are many things that I don't know.

20
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,781
Blooming Abode is just a shop right now

21
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,460
so I can still manage it barely.

22
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,420
But I plan to open more branches

23
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,020
and serve more customers.

24
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:34,860
Mu Dan, you are ambitious and courageous.

25
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,700
I'm sure you can do it.

26
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:39,381
Miss Yun, tell me.

27
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:42,079
Huanyun Pavilion is an inn

28
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,221
that serves food and wine

29
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:45,101
with performances as well.

30
00:02:46,088 --> 00:02:49,040
You have so many activities in your business.

31
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,860
How do you manage all of them?

32
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:52,740
If you want to expand your business,

33
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,541
you can't rely only on yourself.

34
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:57,821
You also need to depend on the capable people around you.

35
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:00,440
Everyone has their strengths

36
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,620
and weaknesses.

37
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,420
You must place everyone

38
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:05,580
in a position that they are best at.

39
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,960
Let your helpers

40
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,661
show their strengths.

41
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,479
My Lord.

42
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,580
I'm extremely grateful

43
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:24,460
for the Princess' love for me

44
00:03:25,159 --> 00:03:26,420
but what I get isn't what I want.

45
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,420
If we are forced to get married,

46
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,120
it will only be unfair to the princess.

47
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,061
I beg you

48
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,300
to cancel my marriage with the princess.

49
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,821
Did you argue with You Zhen?

50
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,880
She has been spoiled since she was young

51
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:47,341
so she has a willful personality.

52
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,580
You should be more accommodating to her.

53
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,580
I've considered it thoroughly.

54
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,740
I didn't ask for this on a whim.

55
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,280
Please agree to my request,

56
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,520
My Lord.

57
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,661
You Zhen is infatuated with you.

58
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:14,061
She begged me a few times for the sake of your position as an official.

59
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:16,461
You are suddenly asking to cancel the marriage now.

60
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,060
Not only have you made her love for you go to waste

61
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:22,981
but you are also neglecting the royal family's reputation.

62
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,940
I broke my promise

63
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,860
regarding the marriage.

64
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,720
I'm willing to resign as assistant revenue minister.

65
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,240
No matter how you punish me,

66
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,820
I have no complaints.

67
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,141
Have you considered it thoroughly?

68
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,680
Yes.

69
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,040
All right.

70
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,380
As a father,

71
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:55,461
You Zhen's happiness

72
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:57,901
has been a worry of mine.

73
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,999
I was worried that you married her

74
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:02,300
for the sake of your career.

75
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,981
However, what you said just now

76
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,060
was the words of a gentleman.

77
00:05:08,959 --> 00:05:11,060
You made me see you in a new light.

78
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,720
Come.

79
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,060
You are a talent.

80
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,461
I'm sure you will achieve something great

81
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,221
after you go through some trials.

82
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:32,260
Well. Let me transfer you to another place first.

83
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,420
Whether you can be promoted

84
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:37,300
will depend on your ability.

85
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,480
Thank you, My Lord.

86
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,380
I'm extremely grateful.

87
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,461
Master!

88
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,781
King Ning has agreed to the cancellation of the marriage.

89
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:08,901
There's no need to persuade anymore, Father.

90
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,280
I must beat you to death!

91
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,820
- Master! - I was unfilial.

92
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:15,141
I'm willing

93
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,581
to accept any of your punishment

94
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,981
but I must remind you, Father.

95
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,740
Lord Chen is entering the capital today.

96
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:23,300
With your abilities,

97
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:24,839
you can persuade him

98
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:26,101
to let you keep your position

99
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,760
and not be hindered by what I did.

100
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,940
Stand up.

101
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,300
It was just an argument

102
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,300
between children.

103
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,879
Liu Shen said

104
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:59,319
he would

105
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:00,740
persuade Liu Chang

106
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:03,940
to reconcile with the princess.

107
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,120
Liu Shen

108
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:10,180
is embarrassed to meet you

109
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:12,740
and begged me to help him

110
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:14,079
offer this month's tribute.

111
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,221
There are nine more boxes outside.

112
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,879
Since Liu Shen

113
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:28,461
became the Grand Treasurer,

114
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,661
the money he offered as tribute

115
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,240
has doubled.

116
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,300
Liu Shen

117
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:36,581
might be a coward

118
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,500
but he is a lapdog who is good at making money.

119
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,981
Your ambition

120
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,940
requires a lot of money to get things done.

121
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,360
Why not

122
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,239
keep Liu as your money tree

123
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:51,021
for now?

124
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,600
Forget it.

125
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:03,661
Since you are willing to say good things about him,

126
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,341
it seems like this person

127
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,820
can win people's hearts.

128
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,680
My Lord, you are wise.

129
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:14,060
Don't worry. He will never be a part of

130
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:15,740
the higher officials' network

131
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:19,341
but there are troublesome people sometimes.

132
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,500
Liu is a good candidate

133
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:23,960
to be sent to protect

134
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,260
the minor officials.

135
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,620
You banished Liu's young master

136
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:40,061
to become an official at a place like that.

137
00:08:40,279 --> 00:08:41,620
I'm sure he can't take it.

138
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,540
In a few days,

139
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:45,301
he will come back and beg for forgiveness.

140
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,860
Then, he'll go and comfort the princess.

141
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,421
How dare he humiliate my daughter.

142
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:54,341
Even if he regrets it in the future,

143
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,181
I must still teach him a lesson

144
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,620
during this period.

145
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,301
She Yan has a good life.

146
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,400
Young Master always

147
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,260
visits the Imperial Stable to choose horses for him.

148
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,199
She Yan risks his life for me

149
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,740
and is busy all the time.

150
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,540
I must prepare a few good horses for him.

151
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,880
You don't travel often

152
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,660
since you're always beside me.

153
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:20,540
Why are you feeling jealous?

154
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,479
That's not right, Young Master.

155
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:24,101
I've worked hard as well.

156
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:26,000
Look. I must fend off assassins

157
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,380
who appear from time to time

158
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:30,061
and have to put up an act together with you.

159
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,720
Fine.

160
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:33,181
I know you've worked hard.

161
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,380
You may take the golden long-poled blade

162
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,759
at the warehouse.

163
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,639
Really?

164
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:41,941
Thank you, Young Master. I will do my best to serve you.

165
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,519
Young Master Liu.

166
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,240
Come.

167
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:59,679
Try this delicious dish.

168
00:09:59,759 --> 00:10:02,140
Official Ge, that's a water ladle used to wash horses.

169
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,701
How can it be used to drink water?

170
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,101
Why not?

171
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,380
Didn't you say it has been cleaned?

172
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:11,319
Are you neglecting your duties?

173
00:10:11,399 --> 00:10:12,740
You are framing me.

174
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,559
Official Ge, why are you troubling me?

175
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:15,639
Why?

176
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,720
Young Master Liu.

177
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,199
You are no longer

178
00:10:19,279 --> 00:10:20,660
King Ning's son-in-law.

179
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,860
There's no need to drink water with a jade ladle.

180
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:24,981
This dirty tool

181
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,061
fits your status.

182
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,301
Pry his mouth open!

183
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,840
Try it.

184
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:34,581
It's very delicious.

185
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,000
Not enough?

186
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,941
How about another ladle?

187
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,120
Official Ge, you are better

188
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,660
at training people than horses.

189
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:49,639
Lord Jiang, why are you here?

190
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,581
The newcomer is disobedient.

191
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,860
Sorry to let you see this, Flower Bird Envoy.

192
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:57,701
Are you here to choose a horse?

193
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,981
Let me bring you there myself.

194
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,200
No need.

195
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,301
I know Zi Shu well.

196
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,639
Let him

197
00:11:04,799 --> 00:11:05,860
accompany me today.

198
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,941
Zi Shu, I'm seeing you in a new light.

199
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,920
You even dare refuse King Ning's wedding proposal.

200
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,960
King Ning used to matchmake you and the princess.

201
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:29,101
Didn't you refuse it as well?

202
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,981
The princess only likes you.

203
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:34,559
In my opinion,

204
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:36,540
she is firm on marrying you.

205
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:38,461
She is so persistent.

206
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:40,821
You could just go with the flow

207
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:41,919
so why did you

208
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,720
ask for trouble instead?

209
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:48,120
Lord Jiang, are you here to persuade me on King Ning's behalf

210
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:50,821
or are you persuading me

211
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,341
for your neighbor's sake?

212
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:57,500
It seems like you miss Jiang Residence's florist a lot.

213
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,320
She faked her death

214
00:12:01,679 --> 00:12:03,061
and restored her identity

215
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:05,660
before establishing Blooming Abode in Chang'an.

216
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,660
I'm sure she had your help.

217
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,821
I'm just investing some capital

218
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,660
to make a profit without doing anything.

219
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,660
She achieved her current success

220
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,101
due to her own capabilities.

221
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,639
Why did you

222
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,421
help her get a divorce

223
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:21,919
in Luoyang?

224
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,421
She was badly bullied by the Liu family.

225
00:12:26,062 --> 00:12:27,920
As her husband, you did nothing

226
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,860
and you wouldn't allow other people to help her?

227
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:34,140
I let her down in the past

228
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:39,861
but I will never be stuck in this stable.

229
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:42,240
When I get promoted,

230
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,900
I will propose to her

231
00:12:44,464 --> 00:12:45,605
and treat her sincerely.

232
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,981
That's a wonderful wish.

233
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:52,800
Have you asked

234
00:12:52,879 --> 00:12:54,341
if He Wei Fang wants that?

235
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,020
I will move her

236
00:12:57,399 --> 00:12:58,660
with my sincerity.

237
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,221
Lord Jiang, why do you

238
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:03,640
care about

239
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,720
who she marries?

240
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:09,301
Are you worried that she can't help you grow flowers and make money

241
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,941
or are you having some selfish thoughts?

242
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,500
That's not important.

243
00:13:20,639 --> 00:13:22,860
But if the princess finds out about your intention,

244
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,440
I'm afraid

245
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,860
Wei Fang's life will be in danger again.

246
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,301
That's all I'm going to say.

247
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:34,020
I hope you behave yourself.

248
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,200
I thank you

249
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:43,679
for what happened just now.

250
00:13:54,039 --> 00:13:55,039
Young Master,

251
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,581
why did you meddle in other people's family business

252
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,981
and make yourself upset?

253
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,540
What do you mean by family business?

254
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,380
They are no longer a family.

255
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,759
Jiang Xiao Hua is my money tree now.

256
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:07,061
You have lots of money in the treasury.

257
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,780
Do you really need this money tree?

258
00:14:20,279 --> 00:14:21,279
You look so pretty.

259
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:24,181
We've purchased Blooming Abode's deed.

260
00:14:24,639 --> 00:14:27,879
You are no longer Qin Wu'er who needs to rely on Wang Qing

261
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,341
but Shopowner Qin who has a shop in Chang'an.

262
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:31,919
You must return to Ning

263
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,101
with your head held high.

264
00:14:35,039 --> 00:14:37,221
I've never returned home

265
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:38,821
in such a grand manner.

266
00:14:39,399 --> 00:14:40,860
Do you think it's too flashy?

267
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,535
Going back in a nice dress will let your family

268
00:14:42,616 --> 00:14:43,814
see you in a different light

269
00:14:43,879 --> 00:14:46,421
and tell them that your life is different.

270
00:14:47,279 --> 00:14:49,301
You are the most successful daughter in the family.

271
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:51,421
You have a great future ahead of you.

272
00:14:51,867 --> 00:14:53,581
They will surely not underestimate you anymore.

273
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,000
Here. Take it.

274
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:58,240
- All right. - Go home bravely.

275
00:15:29,456 --> 00:15:30,479
Father! Mother!

276
00:15:30,559 --> 00:15:31,559
I'm back.

277
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:33,001
- Sister-in-law. Quan'er. - Wu'er.

278
00:15:33,082 --> 00:15:34,198
Wu'er.

279
00:15:34,279 --> 00:15:35,559
- Aunt is back. - Close the door.

280
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,879
Come in quickly. Don't let other people see you.

281
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:49,039
- Give it to me. - A dumped woman still dare return in such a flash way.

