Merchants will normally

560
00:28:57,759 --> 00:28:59,260
send gifts to their major customers.

561
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:01,181
I am your biggest creditor

562
00:29:01,759 --> 00:29:03,060
yet you won't even give me some food.

563
00:29:03,319 --> 00:29:04,319
How can you do business

564
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:05,701
when you are so petty?

565
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:07,280
Who told you I didn't prepare food for you?

566
00:29:07,567 --> 00:29:08,669
These are all for you

567
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:10,221
but not this chicken.

568
00:29:10,302 --> 00:29:11,421
I'm saving it for someone else.

569
00:29:13,119 --> 00:29:14,119
Who is it?

570
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,540
Are you interested in a young man?

571
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:17,941
Should I help you take a look?

572
00:29:18,359 --> 00:29:20,901
When did you see me having an interest in young men?

573
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,661
Sheng Yi is coming back tonight.

574
00:29:24,039 --> 00:29:25,861
I'm sure she is tired after her journey.

575
00:29:26,103 --> 00:29:27,503
I prepared this for her

576
00:29:27,600 --> 00:29:28,781
as a nourishment.

577
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:31,720
Sheng Yi

578
00:29:32,137 --> 00:29:33,381
is always working hard.

579
00:29:33,711 --> 00:29:35,811
She never complains no matter how tired she is.

580
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:39,020
I know she is weak against the cold.

581
00:29:39,519 --> 00:29:41,820
She probably got it when she was with Wang Qing's family.

582
00:29:42,559 --> 00:29:44,701
She wouldn't let Chun take her pulse as well.

583
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,400
So,

584
00:29:46,519 --> 00:29:49,181
I can only take care of her diet.

585
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:53,780
I lived in Jiangnan for a few years when I was a child.

586
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:57,260
Locals wrap chicken in lotus leaf before grilling it.

587
00:29:57,559 --> 00:29:58,559
By doing that,

588
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:00,941
the grilled chicken will have the fragrance of plants.

589
00:30:01,759 --> 00:30:03,661
I heard Physician Chun made medicine

590
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:05,560
and left a few pieces of lotus leaves in your house.

591
00:30:05,799 --> 00:30:07,100
We can give it a try now.

592
00:30:08,039 --> 00:30:09,039
Right.

593
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:21,701
Don't worry.

594
00:30:22,079 --> 00:30:24,221
This is fire. Do you think I dare touch it?

595
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:29,480
You're right.

596
00:30:34,119 --> 00:30:35,300
Don't touch my chicken.

597
00:30:52,759 --> 00:30:53,759
My chicken!

598
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:56,861
Jiang Chang Yang!

599
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:01,880
Young Master.

600
00:31:02,039 --> 00:31:03,621
I've delivered the dendrobium

601
00:31:04,079 --> 00:31:05,901
to the backyard as you ordered.

602
00:31:08,279 --> 00:31:10,260
However, Miss He is still angry.

603
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,580
She even called you

604
00:31:11,839 --> 00:31:12,839
a chicken thief.

605
00:31:14,896 --> 00:31:16,518
The dendrobium was given to me by His Majesty.

606
00:31:16,599 --> 00:31:17,740
It is very precious.

607
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,861
Her mother used to open a medicine shop.

608
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:21,221
I'm sure she knows

609
00:31:21,759 --> 00:31:23,221
this is more nourishing than the chicken.

610
00:31:23,799 --> 00:31:24,799
Why did she still scold me?

611
00:31:25,209 --> 00:31:26,430
Miss He said

612
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:29,022
you should be scolded for taking things away without asking for permission.

613
00:31:30,540 --> 00:31:31,608
Young Master.

614
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:33,560
You knew there was nothing special about the chicken

615
00:31:33,641 --> 00:31:34,981
so why did you steal it?

616
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,200
You know nothing.

617
00:31:36,759 --> 00:31:38,500
I'm doing it for pleasure.

618
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,440
Young Master.

619
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,440
He only said so much

620
00:32:33,871 --> 00:32:35,412
after such a long time.

621
00:32:35,839 --> 00:32:37,381
Most of it is false as well.

622
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:40,381
It's time to take it seriously.

623
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:56,720
Cui Mao.

624
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:59,020
Was the wine I served you

625
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:00,480
strong enough?

626
00:33:02,799 --> 00:33:04,060
Jiang Chang Yang.

627
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:08,060
You've always been putting on an act.

628
00:33:10,279 --> 00:33:11,861
Aren't you afraid

629
00:33:12,759 --> 00:33:15,060
that people might find out that you've brought me here?

630
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:18,319
You knocked out the guards and escaped.

631
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,020
It has nothing to do with me.

632
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:21,940
The officials who escorted you

633
00:33:22,021 --> 00:33:23,718
were worried about being punished for negligence

634
00:33:23,799 --> 00:33:25,340
so he reported that you died from illness.

635
00:33:25,799 --> 00:33:26,799
Right now,

636
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,861
no one knows that you are still alive.

637
00:33:31,119 --> 00:33:32,119
I have a habit.

638
00:33:33,519 --> 00:33:34,758
I will prepare a good jar of wine

639
00:33:34,839 --> 00:33:36,559
to those who enter this place.

640
00:33:37,319 --> 00:33:38,319
If the person is innocent,

641
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:40,580
I will give this jar of wine to him.

642
00:33:41,279 --> 00:33:42,300
If the person is guilty,

643
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,500
I will pour the wine

644
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,461
on his grave.

645
00:33:48,559 --> 00:33:49,740
However,

646
00:33:50,119 --> 00:33:51,141
you wouldn't confess.

647
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:53,060
The wine is already old.

648
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:55,141
I've said

649
00:33:56,359 --> 00:33:57,621
everything I should.

650
00:33:58,231 --> 00:33:59,613
I'm the only one

651
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:01,921
who is responsible for the buying and selling of official positions.

652
00:34:02,359 --> 00:34:03,661
Besides that,

653
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:07,300
I've never committed other crimes.

654
00:34:08,679 --> 00:34:09,679
Is that so?

655
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:23,341
Huameng County's Merchant, Li,

656
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:25,901
had his goods robbed on the 27th day of the third month.

657
00:34:26,559 --> 00:34:29,700
Soon after, his family jade pendant was possessed by Cui Mao.

658
00:34:30,119 --> 00:34:31,261
Li reported it to the officials.

659
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:34,421
That night, his whole family was annihilated by bandits.

660
00:34:35,719 --> 00:34:37,020
The Cui family

661
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:39,381
took 200 mu of Yang's field last autumn.

662
00:34:41,119 --> 00:34:42,119
I forgot to tell you.

663
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:44,180
Those who entered this secret room

664
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:46,020
have never left this place as an innocent man.

665
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,140
If you don't confess,

666
00:34:48,719 --> 00:34:50,341
I will keep finding evidence of your crime.

667
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,880
Robbery and taking other people's land.

668
00:34:53,079 --> 00:34:54,381
Each of those is a serious crime.

669
00:34:55,507 --> 00:34:56,781
You will surely die

670
00:34:57,239 --> 00:34:58,320
but you can choose

671
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,981
to die with less torture.

672
00:35:05,079 --> 00:35:06,341
You still won't confess?

673
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:09,360
Fine.

674
00:35:09,719 --> 00:35:10,781
I'm going to eat supper first.

675
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:37,180
What did you do to my son?

676
00:36:40,480 --> 00:36:41,981
Do you feel helpless?

677
00:36:43,079 --> 00:36:44,079
If you confess,

678
00:36:44,239 --> 00:36:46,100
the mastermind will annihilate your family.

679
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,000
If you don't confess,

680
00:36:48,679 --> 00:36:50,660
you are worried that I will kill your eldest son.

681
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,060
I will take responsibility

682
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,981
for all the crimes.

683
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,440
I beg you.

684
00:36:58,079 --> 00:37:00,180
I beg you not to hurt them.

685
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,781
Your wife and children

686
00:37:04,559 --> 00:37:06,140
know nothing about the crimes you committed.

687
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:08,400
They are not supposed to die

688
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:09,741
for your sake.

689
00:37:16,079 --> 00:37:17,821
If I confess my crime,

690
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:20,580
and the testimony

691
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:21,821
is submitted,

692
00:37:23,599 --> 00:37:25,741
King Ning will know that I'm still alive.

693
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,760
- When the time comes, I... - When the time comes,

694
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:29,560
I would've sent them out of Chang'an.

695
00:37:29,640 --> 00:37:30,660
No one will find them.

696
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:33,941
However, I will send them away

697
00:37:34,599 --> 00:37:36,500
without taking the money you obtained from bribery.

698
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:39,660
In the future, they will live their lives in poverty

699
00:37:40,519 --> 00:37:42,020
but they will also be safe.

700
00:37:49,719 --> 00:37:50,821
During your funeral,

701
00:37:51,920 --> 00:37:53,500
your eldest son was crying without stopping.

702
00:37:55,079 --> 00:37:56,079
I told him

703
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:57,861
I was powerful

704
00:37:58,880 --> 00:38:00,821
and could send this rattledrum to the underworld

705
00:38:01,519 --> 00:38:03,020
and give it to his father.

706
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,760
He believed me

707
00:38:05,639 --> 00:38:07,140
and asked me to send you a message.

708
00:38:09,559 --> 00:38:10,559
He said

709
00:38:11,119 --> 00:38:12,741
he might not be able to see you again

710
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:16,261
but he will miss you forever.

711
00:38:18,119 --> 00:38:20,840
He hopes you can become a good official in your next life

712
00:38:21,679 --> 00:38:23,461
and continue your relationship as father and son.

713
00:39:04,119 --> 00:39:05,119
Sheng Yi.

714
00:39:06,639 --> 00:39:07,781
Sheng Yi, are you asleep?

715
00:39:17,079 --> 00:39:18,079
Sheng Yi.

716
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:20,200
I saw you going back to your room as soon as you returned.

717
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,741
You seemed tired.

718
00:39:22,679 --> 00:39:23,679
Did something happen

719
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:24,981
back at home?

720
00:39:25,559 --> 00:39:26,941
Are you willing to share it with me?

721
00:39:28,120 --> 00:39:30,262
It's still the same with my family.

722
00:39:31,199 --> 00:39:32,421
I have nothing to tell you.

723
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:34,840
Mu Dan.

724
00:39:35,079 --> 00:39:36,079
I'm tired.

725
00:39:36,639 --> 00:39:37,821
I want to rest earlier.

726
00:39:39,039 --> 00:39:40,660
Drink this nourishing soup when it's still hot.

727
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:43,301
You will feel better after drinking it.

728
00:39:44,519 --> 00:39:47,599
Call me any time whenever you want to tell me.

729
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:48,760
Here you go.

730
00:39:50,079 --> 00:39:52,140
You purposely made this for me?

731
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:53,920
What else do you think?

732
00:39:54,199 --> 00:39:55,620
I roasted a chicken for you

733
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,861
but the one next door stole it.

734
00:39:58,519 --> 00:40:01,140
Thankfully, he is sensible and sent this good-quality dendrobium.

735
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,480
Enough talking. Here.

736
00:40:03,639 --> 00:40:04,639
Drink it while it's hot.

737
00:40:09,119 --> 00:40:11,079
Rest early and don't overthink.

738
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:27,159
Young Master, the evidence is ready.

739
00:40:27,239 --> 00:40:28,239
When should we depart?

740
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,741
The sooner, the better.

741
00:40:32,079 --> 00:40:33,220
However, we need an excuse

742
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,000
to go to Luoyang.

743
00:40:37,199 --> 00:40:39,140
His Majesty's teacher has passed away

744
00:40:39,719 --> 00:40:41,140
and is feeling depressed.

745
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:43,240
The Flower Bird Envoy is trying to search for something

746
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:45,060
to ease his mind. How about that?

747
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,440
Call for lunch to be served.

748
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:49,800
Start packing after lunch.

749
00:40:50,599 --> 00:40:51,599
Yes.

750
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:55,440
Lord Jiang.

751
00:41:03,079 --> 00:41:04,079
Miss He.

752
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:11,840
Greetings, Lord Jiang.

753
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:13,861
You were still scolding me last night.

754
00:41:14,679 --> 00:41:15,981
Did you take the wrong medicine today?

755
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:17,861
It was the right medicine.

756
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:20,620
Thank you for delivering the dendrobium last night.

757
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:22,660
Sheng Yi is looking better after eating it.

758
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:25,301
I'm here to give you a gift as thanks.

759
00:41:26,719 --> 00:41:27,941
I only get these few cakes

760
00:41:28,240 --> 00:41:29,941
in exchange for the expensive nourishing herbs?

761
00:41:34,039 --> 00:41:35,039
Enjoy, Lord Jiang.

762
00:41:35,719 --> 00:41:36,719
I'm leaving.

763
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:38,280
Wait.
